This list serves as an inspiration for implementing new features. Not as a definitive list of planned features.

Legend:

i - Implemented
n - Not implemented
p - Partially implemented

General:
i amd64 64-bit mode support
n SMP
n userspace rust std support

Scheduling:
n differentiating between IO-heavy and CPU-heavy processes
n multiprocessor support
n real-time scheduling
n priorities
n priority-inversion handling
n cpu-burst handling

Interrupts:
i general handlers
i system timer
n nested interrupts

Memory Managment:
i basic allocator/deallocator
i paging/virtual memory
n swapping
n thrashing prevention

Interface:
n basic syscalls
n event based programming

Resource managment:
n basic resource manager
n deadlock detection/resolution
